&ldquo;Listen to me. I&rsquo;m the only one you can count on.&rdquo;
&ldquo;&hellip;&hellip;.&rdquo;
&ldquo;I&rsquo;m the only one for you.&rdquo;
&ldquo;&hellip;&hellip;.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Only me.&rdquo;

What an abominable delusion.

* * *

For more than 10 years, my body was possessed by someone else. It would have been nice of &lsquo;that person&rsquo; if she used my body and returned it in a good condition, but not only did she get married with my own body, she&rsquo;s also clinging to her husband like a stalker..?!
&ldquo;First, let&rsquo;s get divorced.&rdquo;
I tried to start a new life by dumping my husband, who has been treating me like tr*sh, and my family who treated me like dirt. But...
&ldquo;Leaving? You will leave me?&rdquo;
My husband who doesn&rsquo;t believe me.
&ldquo;Why are you taking his side, sister?&rdquo;
A younger brother who&rsquo;s suddenly jealous.
&ldquo;Stay in this house. You can&rsquo;t go anywhere.&rdquo;
Even my father who hated me all along is suddenly obsessed? What&rsquo;s wrong with them all of a sudden?
